Module scrabble.main
Package cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.numbers

Interface IOperations

All Superinterfaces:
SType
All Known Implementing Classes:
ScrBinary, ScrFloat, ScrInt
public interface IOperations
extends SType
This interface contains mathematical operations for Scr objects (int and float) It contains additions, subtractions, multiplications and divitions
